{"tid":2236205,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"商人涉8.5當日車停迴旋處 鄭念慈:我裁定係故意堵路 必須判處阻嚇性刑罰 以防患未然 判囚6星期","createTime":"2020-10-09T10:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T01:28:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f460c66d1ad1dbbc884da120e4ff77d72af85901","tid":2236205,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:00:52.000Z","msg":"裁判官鄭念慈:<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FudqwWQkoai1TnMszQKCzrBh2cY=/802x1122/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E24ZJBGNQFGN5OYK4VAKJLHBQI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFudqwWQkoai1TnMszQKCzrBh2cY%3D%2F802x1122%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE24ZJBGNQFGN5OYK4VAKJLHBQI.jpg&h=47526efb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年8.5大三罷當日，中年商人被指將平治房車停泊在九龍城迴旋處慢線「堵路」，被控在公眾地方造成阻礙罪。商人辯稱當時遭另一車輛碰撞，對方不顧而去，故報警停車等候警察到場。惟裁判官鄭念慈不接納被告撞車之說，認為只是煙幕以掩飾堵路真相，裁定罪成，並指堵路行為嚴重影響公眾秩序，對上班市民造成不便，必須判處阻嚇性刑罰，以防患於未然，遂判監六星期。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情透露，被告從事海產貿易生意，惟收入受疫情影響已大不如前，希望法庭考慮案發當日被告的錯誤決定並無造成長時間交通阻塞，並承諾不會再犯。鄭官聞言反駁：「我唔接納錯誤，我裁定係故意堵路。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/7LDTXEXR2ZAQXDAS2LXVEOWNFI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2F7LDTXEXR2ZAQXDAS2LXVEOWNFI%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzhVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=95fdf069\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2F7LDTXEXR2ZAQXDAS2LXVEOWNFI%2F&h=a4e26c3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/7LDTXEXR2ZAQXDAS2LXVEOWNFI/</a>"},{"pid":"d959026a9fa76fabfc2541b974e88ec712396d98","tid":2236205,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\